{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-md-files-js","path":"/[BOJ]-11726-2×n타일링-2/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>0. 문제 링크</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/11726\">>>[BOJ] 11726번: 2xn 타일링&#x3C;&#x3C;</a></p>\n<h1>1. 문제 풀이</h1>\n<p>이런 도형 문제는 그려보는 편이다.</p>\n<p>2x1(세로) 1x2(가로) 2x2(네모) 3개의 도형이 있다.</p>\n<p>dp[i] 는 가로로 i칸이 있음을 의미한다.</p>\n<p><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \" data-url=\"../images/2502162.jpg\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 38.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/0dea83bedbcb72898d6b81df7918ba38/28a80/2502162.webp 400w,\n/static/0dea83bedbcb72898d6b81df7918ba38/8d2ea/2502162.webp 800w,\n/static/0dea83bedbcb72898d6b81df7918ba38/4b075/2502162.webp 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/0dea83bedbcb72898d6b81df7918ba38/4cda9/2502162.jpg 400w,\n/static/0dea83bedbcb72898d6b81df7918ba38/c60e9/2502162.jpg 800w,\n/static/0dea83bedbcb72898d6b81df7918ba38/38b44/2502162.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/0dea83bedbcb72898d6b81df7918ba38/38b44/2502162.jpg\" alt=\"2502162\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그러면 dp[3]을 만들기 위해 또 두 가지로 나눌 수 있다.</p>\n<p>하나는 dp[2] 경우의 수에 2x1 도형을 붙이고 있는 것 과<br>\n다른 하나는 dp[1] 경우의 수에 1x2를 2개 붙인 것과 2x2 1개 붙인 것 이다.</p>\n<p>그렇게 되면 점화식은 아래의 그림과 같아진다.</p>\n<p><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1251px; \" data-url=\"../images/2502161.jpg\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 59.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/1234bc75a954e585d6f4072b8cb0aaa7/28a80/2502161.webp 400w,\n/static/1234bc75a954e585d6f4072b8cb0aaa7/8d2ea/2502161.webp 800w,\n/static/1234bc75a954e585d6f4072b8cb0aaa7/f5742/2502161.webp 1251w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1251px) 100vw, 1251px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/1234bc75a954e585d6f4072b8cb0aaa7/4cda9/2502161.jpg 400w,\n/static/1234bc75a954e585d6f4072b8cb0aaa7/c60e9/2502161.jpg 800w,\n/static/1234bc75a954e585d6f4072b8cb0aaa7/19031/2502161.jpg 1251w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1251px) 100vw, 1251px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/1234bc75a954e585d6f4072b8cb0aaa7/19031/2502161.jpg\" alt=\"2502161\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>2. 전체 풀이</h1>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"a11y-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">package BOJ;\r\n\r\nimport java.io.*;\r\n\r\npublic class BOJ_11727 {\r\n\tpublic static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {\r\n\t\tBufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(System.in));\r\n\t\tBufferedWriter bw = new BufferedWriter(new OutputStreamWriter(System.out));\r\n\r\n\t\tint n = Integer.parseInt(br.readLine());\r\n\r\n\t\tint[] dp = new int[n + 1];\r\n\r\n\t\tdp[1] = 1;\r\n\t\tif (n &lt; 2) {\r\n\t\t\tbw.write(dp[n] + &quot;&quot;);\r\n\t\t} else {\r\n\t\t\tdp[2] = 3;\r\n\r\n\t\t\tfor (int i = 3; i &lt;= n; i++) {\r\n\t\t\t\tdp[i] = (dp[i - 1] + dp[i - 2] * 2) % 10007;\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t\tbw.write(dp[n] + &quot;&quot;);\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tbw.flush();\r\n\t\tbw.close();\r\n\t\tbr.close();\r\n\t}\r\n}</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 16, 2025","title":"[BOJ] 11726번: 2 x n 타일링 2 [JAVA]","tag":"DP","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/[BOJ]-11726-2×n타일링-2"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}